<article class="discover">

  {% include 'discover-nav', labels:'Features,Size,Materials,Specs,Compare' %}

  <div class="max-container">
    <div class="hero has-arrow">
      {% include 'discover-picture', name: heroImg, alt: heroAlt, retina: true, fw: false, lg: true %}
      <div class="hero-content left white">
        <h1 class="title"><span class="subtitle">Discover</span> {{ ctaTitle }}</h1>
        <p class="description">A sleek unisex backpack that converts<br id="prospect-hero-break" /> to a briefcase.</p>
      </div>
      {% include 'hero-jump-btn' %}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">{% include 'hero-jump-target' %}
    <div class="row animate text-center mb-gutter" {{ animateZoomIn }}>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
        {% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-product-image', alt: 'Prospect product shot', retina: true, fw: true, lg: true %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2 class="title">Functional Design Meets Luxury</h2>
          <p>What makes an investment-worthy bag? A precise mix of premium materials and ingenious design features.</p>
          <p><a href="{{ ctaLink }}" class="btn btn-secondary">Buy now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-container">
      <div class="parallax" id="prospect-plax-1"></div>
  </div>
  
  <a id="nav-target-1" class="jumptarget"></a>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
        <div class="topic-content text-center text-left-xs">
          <h2 class="title">A Modern Style</h2>
          <p class="description">The optimum bag for the busy professional, the Prospect goes from office, to airport, to wherever you’re headed next. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="fw-xs">
          {% include 'inline-video', ratio: '3-4', index: 1, poster: 'prospect-feature-1-lg', src: 'Prospect_Discover_Magnet_Revised' %}
        </div>
        <div class="topic-content">
          <h3 class="title">No Velcro, Buckles or Buttons</h3>
          <p class="description">Small but ultra-powerful Rare Earth magnets (made in France!) line the closure of the Prospect, making it both flexible and ultra-secure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-md-6">
        <div class="fw-xs">
          {% include 'inline-video', ratio: '3-4', index: 2, poster: 'prospect-feature-2-lg', src: 'Prospect_Discover_Conversion' %}
        </div>
        <div class="topic-content">
          <h3 class="title">Convertible 2-in-1</h3>
          <p class="description">Carry it as a briefcase in the office, then convert it to a backpack for your commute or travels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> 
  
  <div class="max-container">
    <div class="parallax" id="prospect-plax-2"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mb-default mb-negate-xs mb-negate-sm">
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
        <div class="topic-content text-center text-left-xs">
          <h2 class="title">Fuss-Free Travel</h2>
          <p class="description">Heading straight to the airport? Use the Prospect’s suitcase handle sleeve to seamlessly attach it to your roller bag.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="fw-xs">
          {% include 'inline-video', ratio: '3-4', index: 3, poster: 'prospect-feature-3-lg', src: 'Prospect_Discover_Interior-Organization' %}
        </div>
        <div class="topic-content">
          <h3 class="title">Interior Organization</h3>
          <p class="description">No more sifting! The Prospect has compartments for your laptop, documents, small electronics, and pens.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5 col-md-6">
        <div class="fw-xs">
          {% include 'inline-video', ratio: '3-4', index: 4, poster: 'prospect-feature-4-lg', src: 'Prospect_Discover_Outer-Pockets' %}
        </div>
        <div class="topic-content">
          <h3 class="title">Plenty of Pockets</h3>
          <p class="description">Strategically-designed pockets keep your essentials organized and secure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-container mb-large">
      <div class="topic-block mb-gutter mb-negate-xs">
        {% include 'discover-picture', name: lifestyle1Img, alt: lifestyle1Alt, retina: true, fw: true, lg: true %}
      </div>
      <div class="topic-block" id="prospect-lifestyle">
        {% include 'discover-picture', name: lifestyle2Img, alt: lifestyle2Alt, retina: true, fw: true, lg: true %}
        {% include 'discover-picture', name: lifestyle3Img, alt: lifestyle3Alt, retina: true, fw: true, lg: true %}
      </div>
  </div>

  <a id="nav-target-2" class="jumptarget"></a>

  <div class="max-container topic-block mb-default animate video-block" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
    {% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-video', alt: 'video showing how to pack the Prospect', retina: true, fw: false, lg: true %}
    <a href="#" data-video-id="5" class="video-trigger">See What Fits Inside</a>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mb-large">
    <p><a href="{{ ctaLink }}" class="btn btn-secondary">Buy now</a></p>
  </div>
  
  <a id="nav-target-3" class="jumptarget"></a>
  <div class="container">
    {% include 'discover-section-heading', title: "Premium Materials" %}
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-12 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="fw-xs">
        {% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-materials-1', alt: 'prospect rare earth magnets', retina: true, fw: false, lg: true %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
        <div class="topic-content text-center text-left-xs">
          <h3 class="title">Rare Earth Magnets</h3>
          <p>These ultra-powerful magnets are patented and made in France, by SYSTEMMAG<sup>&reg;</sup>. Commonly found in brands like Nike, the natural elements (neodymium, iron, boron) make them much stronger than regular magnets. Always electronic-safe, they pose zero risk to phones, laptops, or other modern devices.</p>
          <p class="description"><a class="more-window-trigger" href="#magnets-overlay">Read more +</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-12 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="fw-xs">
        {% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-materials-2', alt: 'prospect vachetta leather', retina: true, fw: false, lg: true %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
        <div class="topic-content text-center text-left-xs">
          <h3 class="title">Vachetta Leather</h3>
          <p class="description">Durable and luxuriously smooth, this top-grain leather is vegetable-tanned using natural materials, which are easier on the environment than those used in most tanning processes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-12 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="fw-xs">
          {% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-materials-3', alt: 'prospect 1200D recycled poly material', retina: true, fw: false, lg: true %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
        <div class="topic-content text-center text-left-xs">
          <h3 class="title">1200D Recycled Poly</h3>
          <p class="description">Made from recycled plastic bottles, this technical fabric is water-resistant, eco-friendly, and super-strong. The “D” stands for denier, a measure of yarn thickness, making this recycled poly our thickest and strongest yet.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row animate" {{ animateFadeInUp }}>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-12 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="fw-xs">
          {% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-materials-4', alt: 'Jacquard lining wave pattern', retina: true, fw: false, lg: true %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
        <div class="topic-content text-center text-left-xs">
          <h3 class="title">Wave Jacquard Lining</h3>
          <p class="description">Our founders designed this lining as an homage to their late father, Fred Lo, whose life was full of waves: He was a radio astronomer who loved the ocean.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      
    <a id="nav-target-4" class="jumptarget"></a>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-12 col-md-offset-0">
        <div class="expanding-panels mb-large">
          <div class="panel">
            <button class="toggle collapsed">Specs &amp; Dimensions</button>
            <div class="content">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-default">{% include 'discover-picture', name: 'prospect-dimensions', alt: 'Jacquard lining pattern', retina: true, fw: true, lg: true %}</div>
                <p>The Prospect weighs 3.8 lbs. <br />Laptop insert fits most 15” laptops.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <button class="toggle collapsed">Reviews</button>
            <div class="content">
              {%- assign product = all_products['prospect-1200d-recycled-poly-black-black-grey-wave'] -%}
              {%- include 'pdp-reviews' -%}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <button class="toggle collapsed">Shipping</button>
            <div class="content">
              <p>Free Ground Shipping for all orders $100 and more (before tax and after discounts). Orders below $100 will be charged $7.95 for ground shipping - only available to US addresses. </p>
              <p>Orders can take up to 3-7 business days (does not include holidays and weekends) to be delivered.</p>
              <p>Need it sooner? We also offer expedited shipping quoted directly at checkout (excludes Hawaii, Alaska, U.S. Territories and APO/FPO/DPO addresses). Bulk orders over 10+ units do not qualify for expedited shipping, please contact <a href="mailto:support@loandsons.com">support@loandsons.com</a> should there be any concerns with selecting ground service. Additionally, be sure to add one business day to all expedited shipping estimates, and kindly note we do not ship or process on Saturdays or Sundays.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <button class="toggle collapsed">Warranty</button>
            <div class="content">
              <p>We offer a free one year warranty, which covers product damages/defects. Not to worry though - if your purchase is beyond the year, we do stand by the quality of our products! Please email us at <a href="mailto:support@loandsons.com">support@loandsons.com</a> with a few images of your defective product and someone from our CX team will be sure to assist with your purchase.</p> 
              <p>NOTE: Third party purchases are not covered by our warranty, the original Lo & Sons order number and customer information must be provided.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      
  </div>

  <div id="prospect-cta">
    {% include 'discover-cta', hideSecondaryButton: true, lg: true %}
  </div>

